long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
This extension streamlines your search for Miami-Dade County product approval documents (NOA). Simply enter the NOA number, click 'Open PDF,' and the corresponding document will open in a new tab.

Save Time & Stay Organized

Skip manual searches through webpages.
Quickly access the NOA PDFs you need.
Effortless retrieval for approvals and documentation.
Easy to Use

Intuitive interface for a smooth user experience.
Enter the NOA number and click a button - that's it!
